# Cookies Directory

This directory stores cookies.txt files for authenticating with media platforms.

## Security
- This directory is automatically excluded from web access
- Only the server process can read/write here
- Files should be in Netscape HTTP Cookie format

## Usage
Place your cookies.txt file(s) in this directory. The system will automatically use them when downloading content.

## How to Export Cookies
1. Use browser extension like "Get cookies.txt LOCALLY" (Chrome/Firefox)
2. Export cookies from the site you want to access
3. Save as `cookies.txt` or `platform-cookies.txt` in this folder
4. Ensure file permissions allow server read access

## Supported File Names
- cookies.txt (default)
- youtube-cookies.txt
- instagram-cookies.txt
- Any .txt file will be auto-detected
